=head1 DESCRIPTION

The recommended actions to apply to resolve the issues associated with
your DB instances, DB clusters, and DB parameter groups.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ActionId => Str

The unique identifier of the recommended action.


=head2 ApplyModes => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The methods to apply the recommended action.

Valid values:

=over

=item *

C<manual> - The action requires you to resolve the recommendation
manually.

=item *

C<immediately> - The action is applied immediately.

=item *

C<next-maintainance-window> - The action is applied during the next
scheduled maintainance.

=back



